Package: gdlex-inspector
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: STUDIO GD LEX
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyside6
Description: Read-only disk inspection and prudential reporting tool
 GD LEX Inspector scans disk usage, classifies potentially sensitive data,
 and exports prudential reports. It includes a PySide6 desktop interface.
